blocks.en:
flowchart TD
    A[Client reads beacon on link 1] --> B{Change Count for AP-2 differs from stored?}
    B -- no --> Z[Nothing to do]
    B -- yes --> C{count = old+1 AND All Updates Included = 1?}
    C -- yes --> D[Updated elements already in this frame: just apply]
    C -- no --> E[Refresh: listen for AP-2 beacon OR send Probe Request]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
    A[客户端在链路1读取信标] --> B{AP-2 的变更计数与已存值不同?}
    B -- 否 --> Z[无需处理]
    B -- 是 --> C{计数=旧值+1 且 全部更新已包含=1?}
    C -- 是 --> D[更新元素已在本帧内: 直接应用]
    C -- 否 --> E[刷新: 收听 AP-2 信标 或 发送探测请求]
